node.text:
On April 24th & 25th 2021 @dreamersyouth teamed up with @flycompton & @thebrockfoundation_inc and together created The Gift Of Flight. The Gift Of Flight is a program where we flew over 200 kids in real airplanes exposing them to what Aviation has to offer. Minorities make up less than 3% of the total Aviation career industry professionals, which is an unfortunately low number. 
Our mission is to expose children, especially those within inner city communities to the many career fields where minorities are often underrepresented. Our programs are always free so our families can experience once in a lifetime opportunities without the financial burdens. Thank you to everyone that helped make this happen, @subway & @ralphdiesel for providing healthy lunchboxes and the families that showed up and took part! For more info regarding upcoming events and getting involved please email us: dreamersyouthprogram@gmail.com

King Hussle 
The best to ever do it. A successor in every lane. Really the Greatest. You had niggas pressured here on Earth and got niggas pressured as you reign in Heaven. Some shoes just can’t b filled! Thank you for always going above and beyond. Happy Birthday big brother 💙

node.text:
On April 24th & 25th 2021 @dreamersyouth teamed up with @flycompton & @thebrockfoundation_inc and together created The Gift Of Flight. The Gift Of Flight is a program where we flew over 200 kids in real airplanes exposing them to what Aviation has to offer. Minorities make up less than 3% of the total Aviation career industry professionals, which is an unfortunately low number. 
Our mission is to expose children, especially those within inner city communities to the many career fields where minorities are often underrepresented. Our programs are always free so our families can experience once in a lifetime opportunities without the financial burdens. Thank you to everyone that helped make this happen, @subway & @ralphdiesel for providing healthy lunchboxes and the families that showed up and took part! For more info regarding upcoming events and getting involved please email us: dreamersyouthprogram@gmail.com
